item.title: Maura Healey for governor 2022
item.description: Maura Healey for governor Maura Healey has spent her career standing up for the people of Massachusetts and pursuing justice and equality. Sheâ€™s running for Governor to bring people together and expand economic opportunities for everyone in Massachusetts. Maura has deep roots in Massachusetts. Her parents both grew up in Newburyport. Her maternal grandparents met in Gloucester, where her grandfather worked on the fishing docks and her grandmother, whose ancestors settled on the Parker River in Newbury in 1636, went to nursing school.
